The TCL files here describe the model tree for the SOLPS tree on
solps-mdsplus.

To actually update the model tree:

on lnxb201.aug.ipp.mpg.de (restricted login)

cd /afs/ipp-garching.mpg.de/home/d/dpc/MDS/models
svn up ../TCL/
mdstcl < ../TCL/DIAG_MODEL.TCL
mdstcl < ../TCL/IDENT_MODEL.TCL
mdstcl < ../TCL/MOVIES_MODEL.TCL
mdstcl < ../TCL/SNAPSHOT_MODEL.TCL
mdstcl < ../TCL/SOLPS_MODEL.TCL
mdstcl < ../TCL/TALLIES_MODEL.TCL
mdstcl < ../TCL/TIMEDEP_MODEL.TCL

see also README in /afs/ipp-garching.mpg.de/home/d/dpc/MDS/



